HAZARDOUS ENVIRONMENT COMBAT UNIT (H.E.C.U.)


H.E.C.U. is an elite unit of the US Army created to operate in highly hazardous environments, including anomalous and extreme situations arising from contact with extraterrestrial threats. The H.E.C.U.'s primary goal is to neutralize alien threats and eliminate evidence of Black Mesa Corporation experiments, including any living objects affected by alien technology.

H.E.C.U. operates according to a strict hierarchy and utilizes the most advanced weaponry and tactics: assault rifles, shotguns, sniper rifles, grenades, and armored vehicles. The unit is equipped with highly protective armor and communications equipment to coordinate attacks in challenging locations. They also have specialized equipment for operating in toxic or radioactive areas.